						 <p>You could turn the footnote in the document into a functioning thing with the following minimally kludgy code:</p> <div class="code"> <pre> <code>Seeing as I am only a doctor in whimsy and dado is an expert in medicine^^((bibcite dado))^^, we decided to put our heads together for you all to enjoy.</code> </pre></div> <p>and replacing the current footnote thing with</p> <div class="code"> <pre> <code>[[size x-small]] [[bibliography title=&quot;Footnotes&quot;]] : dado : dado is not licensed to practice medicine in any capacity. [[/bibliography]] [[/size]]</code> </pre></div> 
				 	]]>
